  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SignaNota</strong> is a rogue-like game brought to life with charming pixel graphics.<br><br>In <strong>SignaNota</strong>, a unique '<strong>Slingshot Action'</strong> offers  <br>thrilling battles where a single choice can turn the tide of combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Guide <strong>Signa</strong>, the fallen god of light, and shape her destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your choices will forge a new myth. <br> <br> <br>Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A totally new combat system awaits you. Pull and launch <i>Signa</i>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/a639d241c8817179a78f30af79be94a4.poster.avif?t=1750900002\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/a639d241c8817179a78f30af79be94a4.webm?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/a639d241c8817179a78f30af79be94a4.mp4?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have more than a hundred short - animations! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/11fc0b531bbc8372a676fbdbef1deb7e.poster.avif?t=1750900002\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/11fc0b531bbc8372a676fbdbef1deb7e.webm?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/11fc0b531bbc8372a676fbdbef1deb7e.mp4?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not limited to just one companion. There are six heroines to accompany you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/259eea05b397fafc700a4e6c556e87ed.poster.avif?t=1750900002\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/259eea05b397fafc700a4e6c556e87ed.webm?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/259eea05b397fafc700a4e6c556e87ed.mp4?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple endings. Each heroine offers a unique ending.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/598ac122877a36a86bafb2af3761ac32.poster.avif?t=1750900002\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/598ac122877a36a86bafb2af3761ac32.webm?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/598ac122877a36a86bafb2af3761ac32.mp4?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps, there might even be a hidden ending to uncover.</p></li></ul>",
