i><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not limited to just one companion. There are six heroines to accompany you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/259eea05b397fafc700a4e6c556e87ed.poster.avif?t=1750900002\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/259eea05b397fafc700a4e6c556e87ed.webm?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/259eea05b397fafc700a4e6c556e87ed.mp4?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple endings. Each heroine offers a unique ending.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/598ac122877a36a86bafb2af3761ac32.poster.avif?t=1750900002\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/598ac122877a36a86bafb2af3761ac32.webm?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2974620/extras/598ac122877a36a86bafb2af3761ac32.mp4?t=1750900002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps, there might even be a hidden ending to uncover.</p></li></ul>",
